metadata.name: Schoolbus Graveyard 4x4
metadata.description:
Schoolbus Graveyard 4x4 is a photograph of a spraypaint piece by Adam Toksöz.

It is the first photograph piece, first street art piece minted, and first edition piece on ETH by Adam Toksöz and is the first token minted on the custom $TOKSOZ contract.

Painted at a spot north of Atlanta, GA called Schoolbus Graveyard.

10/10 edition.
